				</div>
				<div class="supermax-detail-grid">
					<article class="supermax-detail-card">
						<h3>Column budget</h3>
						<p>The column budget is the only input that needs to change with the viewport. Supermax fills visible cells by weight and clamps them to each cell's min and max.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="supermax-detail-card">
						<h3>Zoomable anchors</h3>
						<p>When a zoomable cell becomes the anchor, earlier cells can collapse first so the active work area stays readable instead of blindly centered.</p>
					</article>
					<article class="supermax-detail-card">
						<h3>Plain output</h3>
